item.title: How do you Change your environmental variables to your jdk version?
item.dc:creator: @Goodoo_dolls Goodoo dolls
item.description:
@Goodoo_dolls wrote:

Right click computer, Click properties, Click advanced system settings(vista), click the advanced tab, Click enviorment variables then find the class path to the old jdk and change it.
